{"type":"message","id":"aaa04428","parentId":"12daee8f","timestamp":"2026-04-09T03:04:27.249Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:0d879060-9e22-4e9d-88e1-6abbdf5808b3 morning AI bried] Summarize latest AI news from last 24 hours.\n\nFocus on:\n- LLMs\n- RL\n- Diffusion models\n- VLM / robotics\n\nOutput:\n- 5 bullet points\n- Why it matters (2 lines)\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 9th, 2026 — 3:04 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-09 03:04 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1775703867246}}
