{"type":"message","id":"d5f612c8","parentId":"c3f2c170","timestamp":"2026-04-09T03:05:46.206Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"It appears that there was an issue with fetching the content from the URL specified. Let me try a different approach to gather AI news articles.\n\nI'll attempt to search for recent articles on the web using `web_search` again, ensuring it has the necessary API key set up properly.\n\nLet's proceed with fetching AI-related articles from the web:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"freshness\": \"day\",\n  \"query\": \"AI news last 24 hours LLMs RL Diffusion models VLM robotics\"\n}\n```\n\nOnce I have the content, I'll summarize it for you.\n\nIf that still doesn't work, we might consider looking at a different source or method. Let me know how you'd like to proceed.\n```\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_8ab1dddf-994c-4a05-830a-da01dfd90313","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":5,"freshness":"day","query":"AI news last 24 hours LLMs RL Diffusion models VLM robotics"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"qwen-local:latest","usage":{"input":9230,"output":201,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":9431,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775703946206}}
